comments.body:
If I think what you are asking is there a way to take the SKBitmap pixels and turn them into the drawing commands of SKPicture? then no. 

But, if you are just wanting to draw with a matrix, then you should be able to just save the canvas, do the transformation, draw the bitmap and then restore:

```csharp
var canvas = ...;
using (new SKAutoCanvasRestore(canvas)) {
    canvas.Translate(10, 10);
    canvas.DrawBitmap(...);
}
```
